"The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams." -Eleanor Roosevelt
People! I like people, yet strongly believe that the people are in the core of everything.
They are the heart and the soul of each relation and business, they are the future, the hope and the fate.
Because of the people, because I believe in the people I dedicate my life to make a positive difference to someone else life.

Customer-oriented and self-motivated  with experience in customer surviceses and  support. Thoroughly and with attention to detail in daily professional matters, positive attitude and professional approach.
